nd&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;border_color&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;font_color&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;link_color&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-27570\" src=\"https://wpplugin.org/wp-content/uploads/edd/2016/08/2-2.png\" alt=\"2\" width=\"274\" height=\"239\" /></p></div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-w57c0d7dcee02d-4\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" ><div id=\"pgc-w57c0d7dcee02d-4-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"1\" ><div id=\"panel-w57c0d7dcee02d-4-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"7\" data-style=\"{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;widget_css&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;padding&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;background&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;border_color&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;font_color&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;link_color&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\"><h3 class=\"widget-title\">PayPal Fees</h3>\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p>One important note regarding PayPal fees. PayPal charges a fee of 2.2% + $0.30 in the United States for donations (Other counties fees may be different). However currently PayPal doesn\'t specially offer a recurring donation option for developers to integrate with.</p><p>What this means is that the standard PayPal rate of 2.9% + $0.30 will apply when using this plugins recurring donations option (Other counties fees may be different). If the plugin\'s recurring donations options are not used then the standard donation rate will apply.</p></div>\n</div></div></div></div></div>\n\n<style type=\"text/css\" class=\"panels