tes later?</strong><br /> Yes, in the accounts page you can upgrade your license. The license upgrade will be prorated.</p>\n<p><strong>Do I need a business PayPal account?</strong><br /> You can use a Standard PayPal account. A PayPal Business account, which is free, is required for accepeting recurring donations.</p>\n<p><strong>Still have questions?</strong><br /> <a href=\"/contact\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Submit a Presale Question</a>.</p></div>\n</div></div><div id=\"panel-25993-0-0-4\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-last-child\" data-index=\"4\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	\n<hr />\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">Users Also Purchased</h3>\n[downloads ids=\"26,1396,179\" buy_button=\"no\"]\n<hr />\n\n<a name=\"reviews\"></a>\n\n&nbsp;</div>\n</div></div></div></div></div>\n\n<style type=\"text/css\" class=\"panels-style\" data-panels-style-for-post=\"25993\">@import url(https://wpplugin.org/wp-content/plugins/siteorigin-panels/css/front-flex.min.css); #pgc-25993-0-0 { width:100%;width:calc(100% - ( 0 * 30px ) ) } #pl-25993 #panel-25993-0-0-0 , #pl-25993 #panel-25993-0-0-1 , #pl-25993 #panel-25993-0-0-2 , #pl-25993 #panel-25993-0-0-3 , #pl-25993 #panel-25993-0-0-4 {  } #pl-25993 .so-panel , #pl-25993 .so-panel:last-child { margin-bottom:0px } @media (max-width:780px){ #pg-25993-0.panel-no-style, #pg-25993-0.panel-has-style > .panel-row-style { -webkit-flex-direction:column;-ms-flex-direction:column;flex-direction:column } #pg-25993-0 .panel-grid-cell { margin-right:0 } #pg-25993-0 .panel-grid-cell { width:100% } #pl-25993 .panel-grid-cell { padding:0 } #pl-25993 .panel-grid .panel-grid-cell-empty { display:none } #pl-25993 .panel-grid .panel-grid-cell-mobile-last { margin-bottom:0px }  } </style>\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:64:\"Accept recurring donations via PayPal on your WordPress