reenshots</a><br /> <a href=\"#faq\">FAQ</a><br /> <a href=\"#reviews\">Reviews</a></p><hr /><h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">How the Plugin Works</h3><p>Simply install the plugin on your WordPress website, enter your PayPal business information on the settings page, make a new event, then place the shortcode on your site.</p><p>When a customer purchases a ticket, an eTicket will be emailed to them containing a QR code. You as an admin will optionally receive an email notification.</p><p>Use any phone\'s (Android, iOS, Microsoft) QR reader app to scan the customers eTicket and check the customer into the event. When the eTicket is scanned you can see the ticket details such as date purchased, amount and if the ticket has previously been scanned.</p><hr /></div>\n</div></div><div id=\"panel-1396-0-0-1\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_siteorigin-panels-builder\" data-index=\"1\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div id=\"pl-w57bc77744744c\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-w57bc77744744c-0\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;cell_class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;row_css&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;bottom_margin&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;gutter&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;padding&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;row_stretch&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;collapse_order&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;background&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;border_color&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\" ><div id=\"pgc-w57bc77744744c-0-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"1\" ><div id=\"panel-w57bc77744744c-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" data-style=\"{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;widget_css&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;padding&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;background&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:&quot;0&qu