p>What makes this plugin powerful is its simplicity. It has the features you need and not the features you don\'t. You don\'t have to spend days setting up a full eCommerce Solution. In just a few minutes customers from around the world can start buying products or services from your website using PayPal.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr /></div>\n</div></div><div id=\"panel-179-0-0-1\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_siteorigin-panels-builder\" data-index=\"1\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div id=\"pl-w57bc74c8e8a5a\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-w57bc74c8e8a5a-0\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;cell_class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;row_css&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;bottom_margin&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;gutter&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;padding&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;row_stretch&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;collapse_order&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;background&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;border_color&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\" ><div id=\"pgc-w57bc74c8e8a5a-0-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"1\" ><div id=\"panel-w57bc74c8e8a5a-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" data-style=\"{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;widget_css&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;padding&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;background&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;border_color&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;font_color&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;link_color&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p><a name=\"features\"></a></p><h3>Features of the Pro Version</h3></div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-w57bc74c8e8a5a-1\"  class=\"panel-