(4, 1, '2017-04-18 05:00:24', '2017-04-18 05:00:24', '<h2 class=\"secondary-title\"></h2>\r\n<h3>ACCOMMODATION</h3>\r\nKanota Camp with its colonial styled accommodation facilities recreates a time bygone. Rooms include 7 A/C Cottages and 7 Royal Tents and all of them have contemporary amenities for a comfortable stress-free stay. The pristine atmosphere ensures rejuvenation while the cosy rooms make it relaxing.', 'Main Hotel', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'main-hotel-en', '', '', '2018-02-09 09:37:50', '2018-02-09 09:37:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost/hotel/?page_id=4', 0, 'page', '', 0),
