(315, 1, '2017-12-08 05:00:47', '2017-12-08 05:00:47', '<h4><em>Welcome to Kanota Camp where you can experience walking at crack of dawn and witnessing the pleasant surprises of surroundings, located in the neighborhood of Pink City - Jaipur. Here, we offer an excellent solace and relaxation within the lap of Mother Nature. Every morning and evening will reward you with sighting of many migratory birds, fishes ducks………………………</em></h4>\r\n<h4><em>Located by the banks of River Dhund (means misty or foggy), this 6 acre property is perfect for creating beautiful memories. It comes with comforts like cozy accommodations, a well stocked bar, bone fire, lush green gardens and fully-equipped conference room for those meetings that spell business as unusual. There are special attractions for exotic bird sighting (36 ft high watching tower).</em></h4>\r\n<h4><em>The nature has its own charms and beauty. Here you can explore Mother Nature away from the hustle and bustle of the city. Meals, being an opportunity for explorers to share their stories, we offer vegetarian and non vegetarian buffet style meals (including Breakfast, Lunch and Dinner) Indian cuisine.</em></h4>\r\n<h4><em>Kanota Camp ideal place for holiday, picnics, corporate meetings &amp; weddings due to its size, location and offerings. We have the ability to cater for just 10, or events of up to 1000, this certainly making it truly an ideal destination for both leisure and adventure.</em></h4>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '54-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-12-08 05:00:47', '2017-12-08 05:00:47', '', 54, 'http://ambrlabs.com/kanotacamp/54-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
