(340, 1, '2018-02-08 12:02:12', '2018-02-08 12:02:12', 'Welcome to Kanota Camp where you can experience walking at crack of dawn and witnessing the pleasant surprises of surroundings, located in the neighbourhood of Pink City - Jaipur. Here, we offer an excellent solace and relaxation within the lap of Mother Nature. Every morning and evening will reward you with sighting of many migratory birds, fishes and ducks.\r\n\r\nLocated by the banks of River Dhund (means misty or foggy). This 6 acre property is perfect for creating beautiful memories as it comes with comforts like cosy accommodations, a well stocked bar, bone fire, lush green gardens and fully-equipped conference room for those meetings that spell business as unusual. There are special attractions for exotic bird sighting (36 ft high watching tower).', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '54-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-08 12:02:12', '2018-02-08 12:02:12', '', 54, 'http://ambrlabs.com/kanotacamp/54-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
