(376, 1, '2018-02-09 06:40:55', '2018-02-09 06:40:55', 'Jaipur visit is incomplete without shopping. It can enrich your total shopping experience ten-fold. Take the time to scour these places for some of the best fashion and lifestyle options. Check out the exclusive list of shopping places in Jaipur where you should shop until you drop; includes: Johari Bazar (Gemstone Jewellery), Tripolia Bazar (Lac Jewellery), Chandpole Bazar (Marble sculptures), Kishanpole Bazar (wooden souvenirs), Nehru Bazar(Traditional Jooties), Bapu Bazar (Textile goods). It is worth spending a day or two in these markets, located at a distance of 10 KM only.', 'Shopping', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'shopping', '', '', '2018-02-09 06:40:55', '2018-02-09 06:40:55', '', 0, 'http://ambrlabs.com/kanotacamp/?p=376', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(377, 1, '2018-02-09 06:40:55', '2018-02-09 06:40:55', 'Jaipur visit is incomplete without shopping. It can enrich your total shopping experience ten-fold. Take the time to scour these places for some of the best fashion and lifestyle options. Check out the exclusive list of shopping places in Jaipur where you should shop until you drop; includes: Johari Bazar (Gemstone Jewellery), Tripolia Bazar (Lac Jewellery), Chandpole Bazar (Marble sculptures), Kishanpole Bazar (wooden souvenirs), Nehru Bazar(Traditional Jooties), Bapu Bazar (Textile goods). It is worth spending a day or two in these markets, located at a distance of 10 KM only.', 'Shopping', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '376-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-09 06:40:55', '2018-02-09 06:40:55', '', 376, 'http://ambrlabs.com/kanotacamp/376-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(378, 1, '2018-02-09 06:41:35', '2018-02-09 06:41:35', 'The grand Birla temple is located on an elevated ground at the base of Moti Dungari hill in Jaipur, which is also referred as the Laxmi Narayan Temple. Built in pure white marble, the Birla Temple is unlike the traditional ancient Hindu temples, and is built with a modern approach. Inside this magnificent shrine, beautifully sculpted idols of Lord Vishnu and Goddess Lakshmi can be seen. The Birla temple is bordered by lavish green gardens that highlight the splendour of the temple. The regular visiting hours are between, 8.00 AM to 12.00 Noon and 4.00 PM to 8.00 PM every day. This temple is situated within the city and only 11 KM from Kanota Camp.', 'Birla Temple', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'birla-temple', '', '', '2018-02-09 06:41:35', '2018-02-09 06:41:35', '', 0, 'http://ambrlabs.com/kanotacamp/?p=378', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(379, 1, '2018-02-09 06:41:35', '2018-02-09 06:41:35', 'The grand Birla temple is located on an elevated ground at the base of Moti Dungari hill in Jaipur, which is also referred as the Laxmi Narayan Temple. Built in pure white marble, the Birla Temple is unlike the traditional ancient Hindu temples, and is built with a modern approach. Inside this magnificent shrine, beautifully sculpted idols of Lord Vishnu and Goddess Lakshmi can be seen. The Birla temple is bordered by lavish green gardens that highlight the splendour of the temple. The regular visiting hours are between, 8.00 AM to 12.00 Noon and 4.00 PM to 8.00 PM every day. This temple is situated within the city and only 11 KM from Kanota Camp.', 'Birla Temple', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '378-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-09 06:41:35', '2018-02-09 06:41:35', '', 378, 'http://ambrlabs.com/kanotacamp/378-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(380, 1, '2018-02-09 06:42:18', '2018-02-09 06:42:18', 'Jaipur is the first planed city of medieval India and City Palace in Jaipur was once the seat of kings as it was from here that they ruled the region. One of the best tourist spots in the city, the City Palace is a vast complex and includes several buildings, courtyards and gardens. Two of the main palaces in the complex are the Chandra Mahal and the Mubarak Mahal. A must visit destination for tourists is jus 10 KM drive from Kanota Camp.', 'City Palace', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'city-palace', '', '', '2018-02-09 06:42:18', '2018-02-09 06:42:18', '', 0, 'http://ambrlabs.com/kanotacamp/?p=380', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(381, 1, '2018-02-09 06:42:18', '2018-02-09 06:42:18', 'Jaipur is the first planed city of medieval India and City Palace in Jaipur was once the seat of kings as it was from here that they ruled the region. One of the best tourist spots in the city, the City Palace is a vast complex and includes several buildings, courtyards and gardens. Two of the main palaces in the complex are the Chandra Mahal and the Mubarak Mahal. A must visit destination for tourists is jus 10 KM drive from Kanota Camp.', 'City Palace', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '380-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-09 06:42:18', '2018-02-09 06:42:18', '', 380, 'http://ambrlabs.com/kanotacamp/380-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(382, 1, '2018-02-09 06:50:35', '2018-02-09 06:50:35', 'Jaipur\'s most distinctive landmark, the Hawa Mahal is an extraordinary pink-painted delicately honeycombed hive that rises 50 feet. Its unique five-storey exterior has 953 small windows called <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jharokha\">jharokhas</a> decorated with intricate <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Latticework\">latticework</a>. The original intention of the lattice was to allow royal ladies to observe everyday life and festivals celebrated in the street below without being seen. It is particularly striking when viewed early in the morning, lit with the golden light of sunrise. Jus opposite to hawa mahal, you will can grab best Camel Leather products and do window shopping as well. Located in the heart of wall city and jus  – 10 KM away from Kanota Camp.', 'Hawa Mahal', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hawa-mahal', '', '', '2018-02-09 06:50:35', '2018-02-09 06:50:35', '', 0, 'http://ambrlabs.com/kanotacamp/?p=382', 0, 'post', '', 0),
