(474, 1, '2018-02-16 05:56:00', '2018-02-16 05:56:00', 'Welcome to Kanota Camp where you can experience walking at crack of dawn and witnessing the pleasant surprises of surroundings, located in the neighbourhood of Pink City - Jaipur. Here, we offer an excellent solace and relaxation within the lap of Mother Nature. Every morning and evening will reward you with sighting of many migratory birds, fishes and ducks.\r\n\r\nLocated by the banks of River Dhund (means misty or foggy). This 6 acre property is perfect for creating beautiful memories as it comes with comforts like cosy accommodations, a well stocked bar, bone fire, lush green gardens and fully-equipped conference room for those meetings that spell business as unusual. There are special attractions for exotic bird sighting (36 ft high watching tower).\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-450\" src=\"http://ambrlabs.com/kanotacamp/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/16601879_1580609751953889_2210401939009292856_o-300x182.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1108\" height=\"672\" />\r\n<h3>Restaurant</h3>\r\nMeals, being an opportunity for explorers to share their stories, we are offering a feast for your eyes and taste buds. Sumptuous buffets can be savoured inside the spacious, sunlit restaurant or at the outdoor picnic tables. Every breakfast, lunch, and dinner spread is a banquet of hot and cold beverages, barbecued meats, fish, lentils and fresh vegetables garnished and served from our own organic kitchen garden. Making your meal times special are the sounds of the migratory birds. In the evenings enjoy your tea with the river breeze in your hair, and a romantic dinner warmed by the roaring bonfires. Here you can explore Mother Nature away from the hustle and bustle of the city.\r\n\r\nKanota Camp ideal place for holiday, picnics, corporate meetings &amp; weddings due to its size, location and offerings. We have the ability to cater for just 10, or events of up to 1000, this certainly making it truly an ideal destination for both leisure and adventure.', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '54-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-16 05:56:00', '2018-02-16 05:56:00', '', 54, 'http://ambrlabs.com/kanotacamp/54-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
